      Key takeaways

      Microsoft has announced several upgrades for Bing Chat AI, a chatbot that can answer questions, find information, and perform tasks using natural language.23

      Bing Chat AI can now respond with images, charts, and other visual elements to enhance the user experience and provide more relevant and useful answers.3

      Bing Chat AI is also open to everyone, with a sidebar feature in Edge and the promise of third-party plug-ins to extend its functionality and integration.45
